# `@proxed/mail`

Email templates and send utilities (React Email + providers).

## Entry points

- Templates: `packages/mail/src/emails/*`
- Shared email components: `packages/mail/src/emails/components/*`
- Providers: `packages/mail/src/provider/*`
- Template registry: `packages/mail/src/util/templates.ts`
- Send helper: `packages/mail/src/util/send.ts`

## Conventions

- Keep templates pure/deterministic (no fetches inside render).
- When adding a template, register it in `templates.ts` and ensure it has `subjects` for locales.
- Providers should keep side effects contained; use console provider for dev and Resend for prod.

